videos.description: West Virginia's Nathan Adrian spins and hits a jumper early in the first half. The Mountaineers then steal the inbounds pass, and Adrian gets a layup.
videos.headline: Adrian scores four points in less than 10 seconds

videos.description: Daxter Miles Jr. flies in to give the Mountaineers a short lead, but Nazareth Mitrou-Long gives the Cyclones the lead after his fourth 3-pointer of the game.
videos.headline: Myles Jr. flies in, Mitrou-Long buries a 3 for Iowa State

videos.description: With the shot clock running down, Monte Morris gets to the basket for a tough layup against West Virginia
videos.headline: Iowa State's Morris beats the clock with the crossover layup

videos.description: West Virginia's Daxter Miles Jr. steals the ball and passes it ahead to Jevon Carter who has his layup blocked. Miles Jr. is able to retrieve the ball and score at the rim.
videos.headline: Miles Jr. creates turnover, finishes play for West Virginia

videos.description: After Iowa State beats the Mountaineer press, Iowa State's Matt Thomas shoots and air ball which is recovered by West Virginia. The ball gets pushed up to a wide open Daxter Miles Jr. for 3-pointer late in the first half.
videos.headline: Iowa State air ball turns into a 3 for West Virginia

videos.description: West Virginia's Nathan Adrian takes the ball to the basket for a strong layup in the second half against Iowa State.
videos.headline: Adrian goes baseline for the layup

videos.description: West Virginia's Brandon Watkins rejects Iowa State's Matt Thomas emphatically, sending the ball out of bounds
videos.headline: West Virginia's Watkins protects the paint with massive block

videos.description: West Virginia's Sagaba Konate cleans the glass off Tarik Phillip's transition layup miss and scores with a putback dunk.
videos.headline: Konate finishes with big putback flush for West Virginia

videos.description: West Virginia's Elijah Macon corrals a bad Iowa State inbounds pass, sends the ball to Tarik Phillips, who throws it back to Macon down low for the layup.
videos.headline: Macon takes advantage of Cyclones turnover

videos.description: Iowa State, trying to get back into the game, sets up a press. West Virginia sends the ball ahead to Elijah Macon who scores with an easy dunk
videos.headline: Mountaineers break the press for an easy dunk

videos.description: West Virginia Senior Nathan Adrian stops by to break down his and his teammates performance on Senior Day.
videos.headline: West Virginia's Nathan Adrian breaks down Mountaineers Senior Day performance
